            </CardTitle>
          </CardHeader>
          <CardContent>
            <p className="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Departamentos que <strong>atendem</strong> e resolvem chamados. Aparecem na lista "Departamento Respons√°vel" ao criar ticket.
            </p>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>

        <Card>
          <CardHeader>
            <CardTitle className="text-lg text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">
              Departamentos Solicitantes
            </CardTitle>
          </CardHeader>
          <CardContent>
            <p className="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
